{"type":"message","id":"28a77b41","parentId":"dcae6e57","timestamp":"2026-03-24T18:21:59.326Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"进程已终止。现在让我直接验证C2 skip逻辑。从heartbeat-state.json内容看：\n\n- imaBackup.status = \"CRITICAL_ANALYSIS_NEEDED\"\n- imaBackup.nextAttemptSession = 381\n- 当前session应该是379（从pendingActions可知第379次验证）\n\n根据脚本逻辑：\n1. shouldSkipBackup()会检查status是否在optimizationStatuses数组中\n2. 数组包含'CRITICAL_ANALYSIS_NEEDED'\n3. 所以isOptimizationPeriod为true\n4. currentSession (379) < nextAttemptSession (381)\n5. 应该返回true并跳过备份\n\n但是脚本遇到了读取heartbeat-state.json的错误。让我检查脚本中读取文件的代码，看看为什么会出现\"The path argument must be of type string\"错误。\n\n看readHeartbeatState函数：\n```javascript\nfunction readHeartbeatState() {\n    try {\n        const possiblePaths = [\n            path.join(process.env.USERPROFILE, '.openclaw', 'workspace', 'memory', 'heartbeat-state.json'),\n            path.join(process.env.HOME, '.openclaw', 'workspace', 'memory', 'heartbeat-state.json'),\n            path.join('C:', 'Users', 'Administrator', '.openclaw', 'workspace', 'memory', 'heartbeat-state.json'),\n            path.join(process.cwd(), 'memory', 'heartbeat-state.json')\n        ];\n        \n        for (const hbPath of possiblePaths) {\n            if (fs.existsSync(hbPath)) {\n                console.log(`[DEBUG] 读取心跳状态文件: ${hbPath}`);\n                return JSON.parse(fs.readFileSync(hbPath, 'utf-8'));\n            }\n        }\n        \n        console.log('[WARN] 未找到心跳状态文件，尝试所有路径都失败');\n    } catch (e) {\n        console.error('[ERROR] 读取心跳状态失败:', e.message);\n    }\n    return null;\n}\n```\n\n我仔细检查了路径拼接逻辑，各个路径组件都是字符串，应该不会出现类型错误。可能是环境变量问题导致path.join接收到了undefined参数。\n\nprocess.env.USERPROFILE和process.env.HOME在Windows上可能存在差异，需要验证环境变量的实际值。我将检查这些环境变量是否正确定义，确保路径拼接不会出现undefined。\n\nscript中的错误提示很明确：路径参数必须是字符串类型，但实际接收到了undefined。这意味着某个环境变量可能是未定义的，导致path.join无法正常工作。\n\n我需要仔细审查每个路径组件，特别是C盘路径和环境变量，确保它们都是有效的字符串。","thinkingSignature":"reasoning"},{"type":"text","text":"让我直接验证