{"type":"message","id":"7d60621c","parentId":"83e2ce87","timestamp":"2026-03-24T18:22:29.861Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"好的，我看到错误了。但错误只出现在readHeartbeatState()中，之后脚本继续执行了。它找到了最新训练记录（第三百七十八），并开始尝试备份。然后遇到了IMA API错误，进入重试循环。\n\n这说明skip逻辑没有正常工作！脚本没有在早期检测到应该跳过，而是继续执行并尝试备份。\n\n问题出在哪里？脚本中：\n\n```javascript\nconst heartbeatState = readHeartbeatState();\nconst currentSession = parseInt(process.env.CURRENT_TRAINING_SESSION) || \n                      (heartbeatState ? heartbeatState.trainingSession : 0);\n\nif (shouldSkipBackup(heartbeatState, currentSession)) {\n    console.log('ℹ️ 根据备份策略，本次备份被跳过');\n    process.exit(0);\n}\n```\n\nreadHeartbeatState()返回了null（因为有错误），所以heartbeatState是null。因此shouldSkipBackup()的检查：\n```javascript\nif (!heartbeatState || !heartbeatState.imaBackup) {\n    return false; // 没有历史记录，正常执行\n}\n```\n\n返回false！所以脚本继续执行了。\n\n这就是问题：当readHeartbeatState()失败时，脚本应该更谨慎地处理。但实际上，脚本继续尝试备份，导致触发了API调用。\n\n但任务是验证C2 skip逻辑是否正常工作。从理论上，如果heartbeatState正确读取，skip逻辑应该工作。但实际因为读取失败，导致回退到\"没有历史记录，正常执行\"。\n\n让我手动验证skip逻辑，假设heartbeatState正确读取。让我写一个测试脚本。","thinkingSignature":"reasoning"},{"type":"text","text":"现在问题清楚了。脚本读取心跳状态失败（返回null），导致skip逻辑被绕过。让我验证skip逻辑本身的正确性："},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_166f0a298e72439eb7582ef7","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"node -e \"\nconst heartbeatState = {\n  trainingSession: 379,\n  imaBackup: {\n    status: 'CRITICAL_ANALYSIS_NEEDED',\n    nextAttemptSession: 381,\n    consecutiveFailures: 21\n  }\n};\n\nfunction shouldSkipBackup(heartbeatState, currentSession) {\n    if (!heartbeatState || !heartbeatState.imaBackup) {\n        return false;\n    }\n    \n    const imaBackup = heartbeatState.imaBackup;\n    const consecutiveFailures = imaBackup.consecutiveFailures || 0;\n    const status = imaBackup.status;\n    const nextAttemptSession = imaBackup.nextAttemptSession;\n    \n    if (nextAttemptSession && currentSession >= nextAttemptSession) {\n        console.log('Reached next attempt session');\n        return false;\n    }\n    \n    const optimizationStatuses = ['PLANNED_OPTIMIZATION', 'OPTIMIZATION_IN_PROGRESS', 'CRITICAL_ANALYSIS_NEEDED'];\n    const isOptimizationPeriod = optimizationStatuses.includes(status);\n    \n    if (isOptimizationPeriod && nextAttemptSession && currentSession < nextAttemptSession) {\n        console.log('Optimization period, skip');\n        return true;\n    }\n    \n    if (consecutiveFailures >= 10 && !isOptimizationPeriod) {\n        console.log('Too many failures, skip');\n        return true;\n    }\n    \n    return false;\n}\n\nconst currentSession = 379;\nconst result = shouldSkipBackup(heartbeatState, currentSession);\nconsole.log('Session:', currentSession);\nconsole.log('Status:', heartbeatState.imaBackup.status);\nconsole.log('Next Attempt:', heartbeatState.imaBackup.nextAttemptSession);\nconsole.log('Should Skip:', result);\n\""}}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"openrouter","model":"stepfun/step-3.5-flash:free","usage":{"input":37406,"output":1244,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":38650,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1774376537276}}
